co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib

Interface ObjectStore<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of objects in the store
    All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, BatchReadable<byte[],T>, BatchWritable<byte[],T>, Closeable, Dataset

    @Beta
public interface ObjectStore<T>
extends Dataset, BatchReadable<byte[],T>, BatchWritable<byte[],T>
    A dataset that stores objects of a particular class into a table.

    Supported types are:

    • a plain java class
    • a parametrized class
    • a static inner class of one of the above

    Interfaces and not-static inner classes are not supported. An ObjectStore will serialize the entire object and store it in a single column. See ObjectMappedTable if you want object fields to be mapped to their own columns.
